queries: select cal.partition_date as fecha_proceso, 'R0740363' as cod_incidencia, count(*) as num_reg_total, sum(case when rpad(' ', 40, ' ') = cal.e0665_califmae then 1 else 0  end)  as num_reg_error, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as op_timestamp, 'bi_corp_bdr.jm_cal_emision' as tabla from bi_corp_bdr.jm_cal_emision cal where cal.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by  cal.partition_date

select cal.partition_date as fecha_proceso, 'R0130363' as cod_incidencia, count(1) as num_reg_total, sum(case when cal_aux.num_reg_error > 1 then 1 else 0 end ) as num_reg_error  , from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as op_timestamp, 'bi_corp_bdr.jm_cal_emision' as tabla from bi_corp_bdr.jm_cal_emision cal left join (select count(1) as num_reg_error, cal1.e0665_califmae, cal1.e0665_s1emp , cal1.e0665_cod_emis ,cal1.e0665_id_emisi, cal1.e0665_cod_agen, cal1.e0665_ccodplz, cal1.partition_date from bi_corp_bdr.jm_cal_emision cal1 where cal1.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by cal1.e0665_califmae, cal1.e0665_s1emp , cal1.e0665_cod_emis , cal1.e0665_id_emisi , cal1.partition_date , cal1.e0665_cod_agen , cal1.partition_date , cal1.e0665_ccodplz having count (1) > 1) cal_aux on cal.e0665_califmae = cal_aux.e0665_califmae and cal.e0665_s1emp = cal_aux.e0665_s1emp and cal.e0665_cod_emis = cal_aux.e0665_cod_emis and cal.e0665_id_emisi = cal_aux.e0665_id_emisi and cal.partition_date = cal_aux.partition_date and cal.e0665_cod_agen = cal_aux.e0665_cod_agen and cal.e0665_ccodplz  = cal_aux.e0665_ccodplz where cal.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by  cal.partition_date
